======================================================================
5. SYSTEM ARCHITECTURE
======================================================================
High-level flow:
1) User interacts with Next.js frontend.
2) Frontend calls backend REST API at /api/*.
3) Backend enforces JWT auth, role guards, validation, and business rules.
4) Data persists in MySQL.
5) Razorpay handles payment collection; backend verifies signatures.
6) Backend updates donation and campaign totals, sends email receipt.

Primary components:
- Frontend UI and role-based dashboards
- Backend API controllers and middleware
- MySQL relational schema for users/campaigns/donations/expenses
- Optional local or S3-backed file uploads

======================================================================
