10. SECURITY AND COMPLIANCE CONTROLS
======================================================================
Implemented controls:
- JWT-protected endpoints for authenticated actions
- Role-based authorization guard
- Input validation via express-validator
- Helmet security headers
- Rate limiting (auth-focused + global)
- Payment signature verification using HMAC
- File upload restrictions and middleware-level handling

Observations:
- Environment secret loading is enforced for JWT secret
- API includes dedicated health endpoint for monitoring

